{
  "stem": "14060.9",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So there wasn't a single person-- and I maintain that very strongly, and I don't care what anybody says-- who went through it and came back with the same belief and conviction, without any doubt or question , as they went there.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't believe it if anybody tells you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They may have done shiva, they may have even become more religious and more Hasidic, even become rebbes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't care.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But that-- this event has weakened a certain link-- in some more, in some less-- in the unshakable belief of God and religion.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I have no doubt about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I always say, when certain things are discussed-- this can't happen or can't be done-- and my answer to them is, everything can happen and everything can be done.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It only needs the circumstances to be like that, and it can happen.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that is human nature.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I'm sorry I was philosophizing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Anyway, I got back on this transport to Passau, which is the upper end of the Inn.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And, stupidly enough, in my condition, I went swimming.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I caught, promptly, a pneumonia.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And by the time we got to Linz, in Austria, I was in the crisis day of my pneumonia and the group threatened to leave me behind.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I told them not to do it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But-- and they-- we went out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "For two days I was in a railway wagon on Linz railway station going through a very high-temperature pneumonia.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But not even a doctor.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I don't even remember what-- any medicine.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Maybe I got some tablets or whatnot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And then we went out, shortly, the day after, two days after, to Innsbruck, which was the Russian-American border in the partition of Austria.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
